## Animations and Transitions

### CSS Transitions

```css
/* Standard Transition */
.transition {
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

/* Common Transitions */
.fade-in {
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  opacity: 1;
}

.fade-out {
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  opacity: 0;
}

.slide-up {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
  transform: translateY(0);
  opacity: 1;
}

.slide-down {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
  transform: translateY(10px);
  opacity: 0;
}
```

### CSS Animations

```css
